docs/qa-runs/
docs/*session*.md
docs/*verification*.md
docs/launch-readiness-20*.md
docs/launch-readiness-gap-audit-*.md
docs/*.png
docs/ui-screenshots-*/

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts
templates/pdf-to-json/__pycache__/

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
